:a88a9680-88c0-48ff-b2d6-48812e4408bf
        a                   obo:ECO_0000353 , owl:NamedIndividual ;
        rdfs:comment        "Binds Ngfr (Q9Z0W1)  nerve growth factor receptor. Also forms dimer with Zfp110  (Nrif1) Q9QZ07. The authors also suggest that Zfp369 can form homodimers with itself because in a Nrif1 deletion  levels of Zfp369 are up  and they have already demonstrated" ;
        lego:evidence-with  "PR:Q9Z0W1" ;
